{"tid":1647710,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"（中共霸權）時代革命被禁","createTime":"2019-10-12T00:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T04:59:54.000Z","uid":2104,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8cb936079529f905d98db7bf840b99cdf3bfcb50","tid":1647710,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:57:20.000Z","msg":"Google 宣佈以「禁止手遊開發商利用仍進行中的衝突謀利」為由，把一款以香港示威為背景的角色扮演手機遊戲程式 &mdash;「The Revolution of Our Times 1」( 時代革命 1 ) 從 Google Play Store下架。Google 發言人指該手機遊戲利用敏感事件，即仍發展中的嚴重衝突和災難來賺取利潤，違反了 Google 政策。<br />\n <br />\n「The Revolution of Our Times 1」是一款文字 RPG 遊戲，故事以香港反送中運動為背景，讓玩家扮演示威者，就每件事作出抉擇，而每個決定都會影響民意、玩家能力、屬性等，並影響遊戲結局。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CM09Jtf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCM09Jtf.png&h=9a077028&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3LU6LGB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3LU6LGB.png&h=e96915ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RQ9iBOh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRQ9iBOh.png&h=0029596f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲開發者 Spinner of Yarns 昨日接受《立場新聞》訪問時表示 3 日前接獲 Google 電郵，指敏感事件政策（Sensitive Events policy）列明手機程式不應利用自然災害、暴行、悲劇等賺取利潤，要將其遊戲下架。<br />\n <br />\nSpinner of Yarns 強調遊戲八成的收入都會捐予星火同盟支援被捕示威者，因此已向 Google 提出上訴，正等候對方回覆。他亦要求 Google 解釋為何香港示威活動屬於敏感事件，質疑 Google 是否已經「跪低」。<br />\n <br />\n在本星期，Apple 亦宣佈把應用程式「HKmap.live」下架，指該 APP 侵害香港警察。不過，Google認為「HKmap.live」沒有違反公司政策，該 APP 在 Google Play Store 仍可下載。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/10/11/the-revolution-of-our-times-google-play/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F10%2F11%2Fthe-revolution-of-our-times-google-play%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=d6909698\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/10/11/the-revolution-of-our-times-google-play/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共霸權！全球需要聯合反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45b1ef9b21beb880b23bcd505368ce49ac4f1f6","tid":1647710,"uid":110332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:01:08.000Z","msg":"救命唔想以後瞓唔到<br />\n100%預言！被報夢！原來關自己人事！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1647687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1647687</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d7d00ecad1fc6b0551e2e1672b6e20751cfdb462","tid":1647710,"uid":322230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:04:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">合法公民抗爭！！！！<br />\n咁你都唔郁？？？？？<br />\n唔撚洗想贏！！！！！<br />\n入黎跟住做啦！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1637669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1637669</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 唞夠未？？？<br />\n今日 <br />\n反緊急法遊行 <br />\n尖沙咀鐘樓 <br />\n15.00 見<br />\n15.00 見<br />\n15.00 見<br />\n15.00 見<br />\n15.00 見</span></em></span>"},{"pid":"0278f661ed60d5e718e1ed634061f6f118f5d4a1","tid":1647710,"uid":176447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:05:34.000Z","msg":"八成收入 兩成人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b410a8e5c42459bd61e586e4f37b30c1041cf75","tid":1647710,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0278f661ed60d5e718e1ed634061f6f118f5d4a1","tid":1647710,"uid":176447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:05:34.000Z","msg":"八成收入 兩成人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:15:21.000Z","msg":"肥過肥仔水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06df23a7c178576614cfee6008d8c1b4b18e08d1","tid":1647710,"uid":1477,"like